          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Magic",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". As previously mentioned, each character has a unique gameplay style depending on which cards you draft during your run. In addition, they have cross compatibility with each of the other characters, so test out all of the combinations and find a strategy that works best for your own brand of gameplay.",
